="00:12.227" end="00:13.995"><span begin="00:12.227" end="00:12.958">( Oh-</span><span begin="00:12.958" end="00:13.995">oh)</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">毫无生气的眼神</span></p><p begin="00:12.085" end="00:13.404" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:12.085" end="00:12.255">Till</span> <span begin="00:12.255" end="00:12.434">the</span> <span begin="00:12.434" end="00:12.701">day</span> <span begin="00:12.701" end="00:12.818">that</span> <span begin="00:12.818" end="00:12.998">I</span> <span begin="00:12.998" end="00:13.404">die</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到我离开人世的那一天</span></p><p begin="00:13.434" end="00:15.465" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:13.434" end="00:14.200">Dead</span> <span begin="00:14.200" end="00:14.894">in</span><span begin="00:14.894" end="00:15.465">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">心如死灰</span></p><p begin="00:15.465" end="00:16.672" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:15.465" end="00:15.605">I</span> <span begin="00:15.605" end="00:15.776">just</span> <span begin="00:15.776" end="00:15.973">wanna</span> <span begin="00:15.973" end="00:16.152">feel</span> <span begin="00:16.152" end="00:16.672">alive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只想感受到生命的活力</span></p><p begin="00:16.735" end="00:18.850" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:16.735" end="00:17.210">With</span> <span begin="00:17.210" end="00:17.572">you,</span> <span begin="00:17.572" end="00:18.155">I'm</span> <span begin="00:18.155" end="00:18.850">alive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">与你在一起 我充满活力</span></p><p begin="00:18.850" end="00:19.945" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:18.850" end="00:19.104">With</span> <span begin="00:19.104" end="00:19.312">you,</span> <span begin="00:19.312" end="00:19.535">I'm</span> <span begin="00:19.535" end="00:19.945">alive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">与你在一起 我充满活力</span></p><p begin="00:20.051" end="00:23.153" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:20.051" end="00:20.497">Fell</span> <span begin="00:20.497" end="00:20.881">in</span> <span begin="00:20.881" end="00:21.305">love</span> <span begin="00:21.305" end="00:21.578">but</span> <span begin="00:21.578" end="00:21.744">it</span> <span begin="00:21.744" end="00:22.122">left</span> <span begin="00:22.122" end="00:22.537">me</span> <span begin="00:22.537" end="00:23.153">lonely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坠入爱河 我却感觉孤单不已</span></p><p begin="00:23.358" end="00:26.698" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:23.358" end="00:23.761">Tried</span> <span begin="00:23.761" end="00:24.197">to</span> <span begin="00:24.197" end="00:24.594">trust,</span> <span begin="00:24.594" end="00:24.888">but</span> <span begin="00:24.888" end="00:25.076">it</span> <span begin="00:25.076" end="00:25.478">burned</span> <span begin="00:25.478" end="00:25.747">me</span> <span begin="00:25.747" end="00:26.698">slowly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试图信任 却慢慢地让我饱受煎熬</span></p><p begin="00:27.435" end="00:30.395" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:27.435" end="00:27.619">I</span> <span begin="00:27.619" end="00:28.162">didn't</span> <span begin="00:28.162" end="00:28.690">know</span> <span begin="00:28.690" end="00:28.877">what</span> <span begin="00:28.877" end="00:29.050">I</span> <span begin="00:29.050" end="00:29.330">was</span> <span begin="00:29.330" end="00:29.884">looking</span> <span begin="00:29.884" end="00:30.395">for</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不知道我在寻找什么</span></p><p begin="00:30.874" end="00:37.541" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:30.874" end="00:31.754">Till</span> <span begin="00:31.754" end="00:32.610">I</span> <span begin="00:32.610" end="00:33.434">found</span> <span begin="00:33.434" end="00:37.541">her</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到我遇见她</span></p><p begin="00:38.434" end="00:44.735" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:38.434" end="00:39.314">I</span> <span begin="00:39.314" end="00:40.162">found</span> <span begin="00:40.162" end="00:44.735">her</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我遇见她</span></p><p begin="00:45.087" end="00:51.217" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:45.087" end="00:45.859">With</span><span begin="00:45.859" end="00:46.734">out</span> <span begin="00:46.734" end="00:51.217">her</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没有她</span></p><p begin="00:47.327" end="00:47.980" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:47.327" end="00:47.471">I'm</span> <span begin="00:47.471" end="00:47.618">a</span> <span begin="00:47.618" end="00:47.980">mess</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我狼狈不堪</span></p><p begin="00:48.244" end="00:50.396" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:48.244" end="00:48.391">There</span> <span begin="00:48.391" end="00:48.532">was</span> <span begin="00:48.532" end="00:48.627">nothing</span> <span begin="00:48.627" end="00:48.900">about</span> <span begin="00:48.900" end="00:49.212">that</span> <span begin="00:49.212" end="00:49.515">love</span> <span begin="00:49.515" end="00:49.761">that</span> <span begin="00:49.761" end="00:50.060">made</span> <span begin="00:50.060" end="00:50.396">sense</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这份爱毫无意义可言</span></p><p begin="00:50.625" end="00:51.245" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:50.625" end="00:50.772">I</span> <span begin="00:50.772" end="00:50.918">was</span> <span begin="00:50.918" end="00:51.245">stressed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我焦虑不安</span></p><p begin="00:51.461" end="00:57.747" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:51.461" end="00:51.725">Till</span> <span begin="00:51.725" end="00:52.540">I</span> <span begin="00:52.540" end="00:53.372">found</span> <span begin="00:53.372" end="00:56.901">her</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:54.639" end="00:57.747"><span begin="00:54.639" end="00:55.414">(Oh-</span><span begin="00:55.414" end="00:56.076">oh,</span> <span begin="00:56.315" end="00:57.024">oh-</span><span begin="00:57.024" end="00:57.747">oh)</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到我遇见她</span></p><p begin="01:00.003" end="01:01.729" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:00.003" end="01:00.479">I've</span> <span begin="01:00.479" end="01:00.774">run</span> <span begin="01:00.774" end="01:00.917">for</span> <span begin="01:00.917" end="01:01.300">many</span> <span begin="01:01.300" end="01:01.729">miles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我走过漫漫长路</span></p><p begin="01:01.691" end="01:04.906" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:01.691" end="01:02.003">Trying</span> <span begin="01:02.003" end="01:02.319">to</span> <span begin="01:02.319" end="01:02.571">find</span> <span begin="01:02.571" end="01:03.005">love</span> <span begin="01:03.005" end="01:03.273">from</span> <span begin="01:03.273" end="01:03.429">a</span> <span begin="01:03.429" end="01:03.687">woman</span> <span begin="01:03.687" end="01:03.976">that</span> <span begin="01:03.976" end="01:04.228">could</span> <span begin="01:04.228" end="01:04.645">love</span> <span begin="01:04.645" end="01:04.906">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试图从一位能够好好爱我的女孩身上寻找爱意</span></p><p begin="01:04.906" end="01:06.271" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:04.906" end="01:05.122">And</span> <span begin="01:05.122" end="01:05.411">never</span> <span begin="01:05.411" end="01:05.706">leave</span> <span begin="01:05.706" end="01:05.974">my</span> <span begin="01:05.974" end="01:06.271">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远不会离开我身边</span></p><p begin="01:06.687" end="01:08.405" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:06.687" end="01:06.832">And</span> <span begin="01:06.832" end="01:07.159">I've</span> <span begin="01:07.159" end="01:07.432">run</span> <span begin="01:07.432" end="01:07.600">for</span> <span begin="01:07.600" end="01:07.983">many</span> <span begin="01:07.983" end="01:08.405">miles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我已走过漫漫长路</span></p><p begin="01:08.405" end="01:11.637" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:08.405" end="01:08.747">Trying</span> <span begin="01:08.747" end="01:09.011">to</span> <span begin="01:09.011" end="01:09.261">get</span> <span begin="01:09.261" end="01:09.715">away</span> <span begin="01:09.715" end="01:09.963">from</span> <span begin="01:09.963" end="01:10.133">the</span> <span begin="01:10.133" end="01:10.389">things</span> <span begin="01:10.389" end="01:10.773">I'm</span> <span begin="01:10.773" end="01:11.245">afraid</span> <span begin="01:11.245" end="01:11.637">of</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试图远离我害怕的东西</span></p><p begin="01:11.637" end="01:13.797" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:11.637" end="01:11.788">And</span> <span begin="01:11.788" end="01:12.321">everything</span> <span begin="01:12.321" end="01:12.538">in</span><span begin="01:12.538" end="01:13.797">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">以及我内心深处的一切</span></p><p begin="01:14.248" end="01:15.722" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:14.248" end="01:14.375">You</span> <span begin="01:14.375" end="01:14.519">say</span> <span begin="01:14.519" end="01:14.664">that</span> <span begin="01:14.664" end="01:14.851">we're</span> <span begin="01:14.851" end="01:15.104">already</span> <span begin="01:15.104" end="01:15.421">done</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:15.452" end="01:15.722"><span begin="01:15.452" end="01:15.722">(Done)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">分道扬镳</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你说我们已经分道扬镳</span></p><p begin="01:15.670" end="01:17.006" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:15.670" end="01:15.911">But</span> <span begin="01:15.885" end="01:16.045">what</span> <span begin="01:16.045" end="01:16.213">does</span> <span begin="01:16.213" end="01:16.373">that</span> <span begin="01:16.373" end="01:16.628">even</span> <span begin="01:16.628" end="01:17.006">mean?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但这究竟是什么意思</span></p><p begin="01:17.429" end="01:18.853" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="01:17.429" end="01:17.614">You</span> <span begin="01:17.614" end="01:17.774">tell</span> <span begin="01:17.774" end="01:17.929">me</span> <span begin="01:17.929" end="01:18.101">to</span> <span begin="01:18.101" end="01:18.325">open</span> <span begin="01:18.325" end="01:18.477">my</span> <span begin="01:18.477" end="01:18.853">eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你告诉我睁开双眼</span></p><p begin="01:19.229" end="01:20.342" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="01:19.229" end="01:19.381">Thank</span> <span begin="01:19.381" end="01:19.527">God</span> <span begin="01:19.527" end="01:19.653">it</span> <span begin="01:19.653" end="01:19.805">was</span> <span begin="01:19.805" end="01:19.953">just</span> <span begin="01:19.953" end="01:20.096">a</span> <span begin="01:20.096" end="01:20.342">dream</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">感谢上帝 这只是一场梦</span></p><p begin="01:20.678" end="01:22.185" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="01:20.678" end="01:20.856">I</span> <span begin="01:20.856" end="01:21.000">guess</span> <span begin="01:21.000" end="01:21.152">that's</span> <span begin="01:21.152" end="01:21.303">how</span> <span begin="01:21.303" end="01:21.447">you</span> <span begin="01:21.447" end="01:21.590">know</span> <span begin="01:21.590" end="01:21.742">that</span> <span begin="01:21.742" end="01:21.886">it's</span> <span begin="01:21.886" end="01:22.185">love</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想这就是你知道这是爱的原因</span></p><p begin="01:22.389" end="01:23.469" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="01:22.389" end="01:22.536">When</span> <span begin="01:22.536" end="01:22.568">you're</span> <span begin="01:22.568" end="01:22.722">scared</span> <span begin="01:22.722" end="01:22.872">to</span> <span begin="01:22.872" end="01:23.065">death,</span> <span begin="01:23.065" end="01:23.237">they'll</span> <span begin="01:23.237" end="01:23.469">leave</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当你心生恐惧 他们会离去</span></p><p begin="01:23.966" end="01:26.120" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="01:23.966" end="01:24.165">Just</span> <span begin="01:24.165" end="01:24.389">say</span> <span begin="01:24.389" end="01:24.541">that</span> <span begin="01:24.541" end="01:24.701">you'll</span> <span begin="01:24.701" end="01:24.933">never</span> <span begin="01:24.933" end="01:25.301">leave,</span> <span begin="01:25.669" end="01:25.798">never</span> <span begin="01:25.798" end="01:26.120">leave</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要说你永远不离不弃</span></p><p begin="01:26.188" end="01:28.816" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="01:26.188" end="01:26.700">Baby,</span> <span begin="01:26.700" end="01:27.582">hold</span> <span begin="01:27.582" end="01:28.461">me</span> <span begin="01:28.461" end="01:28.816">close</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝 紧紧地拥抱我</span></p><p begin="01:28.816" end="01:29.973" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="01:28.816" end="01:28.976">Look</span> <span begin="01:28.976" end="01:29.120">me</span> <span begin="01:29.120" end="01:29.368">dead</span> <span begin="01:29.368" end="01:29.512">in</span> <span begin="01:29.512" end="01:29.712">my</span> <span begin="01:29.712" end="01:29.973">eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">注视着我毫无生气的眼神</span></p><p begin="01:29.973" end="01:32.436" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="01:29.973" end="01:30.749">Dead</span> <span begin="01:30.749" end="01:31.7